This will probably have to be released again. 3.4.5

* Upgrade task to convert \{activity-stream\} to \{gadget....\}
* Write functional tests to ensure it works

If users [remove SVN permissions for the root path|http://test.jira.com/secure/admin/RepositoryProjectList.jspa] it will stop bamboo from creating new plans, failing with:
{noformat}
This is not a valid Subversion Repository: svn: Authentication required for '<https://test.jira.com:443> Subversion Repository'
{noformat}


This is because it removes read permission on root for _bamboo-svn-user - see also AOD-1557.
